## How to Create New Phase Documentation

1. **Phase Start:**
   ```bash
   # Create plan
   echo "# Phase {N}: {TITLE}" > docs/phases/PHASE{N}_{TITLE}_PLAN.md

   # Update TODO
   echo "### Phase {N}: {TITLE}" >> TRAVEL_DETAILS_TODO.md
   ```

2. **During Phase:**
   - Keep phase status updated in TRAVEL_DETAILS_TODO.md
   - Update metrics as you progress
   - Document blockers

3. **Phase End:**
   - Create PHASE{N}_*.md files
   - Generate completion report
   - Move docs to docs/phases/
   - Update guides in docs/guides/

